thread.title: Jacob

author: Jacob
title: Jacob
text: The screen printing kit arrived quickly and everything was accounted for. I've screen printed before and just needed the basics to get started again. The press was easy to set up, but you do need to mount it to a solid table or bench. The supplies I've used so far are of good quality and I have no complaints. I look forward to ordering more from ScreenPrinting dot com in the future.
